  "abstract": "The beneficial aspects of legumes in sustainable cropping systems have long been known\r\nand extensively documented. Although grain legumes generally contribute less fixed N\r\nthan pasture legumes, due to removal from the field of grain and stover of grain legumes,\r\nthere is increasing evidence of their positi\"e contribution to N balances and increased yields\r\n",
